{"lineNumber":175937,"originalJapaneseLine":"　……マヨネーズ隊だったか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"...the Mayonnaise Squad, was it?\""},

{"lineNumber":175938,"originalJapaneseLine":"「マエリータ隊だ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's the Maelita Squad!"},

{"lineNumber":175939,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今、そう名乗っただろうが！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"I just said so, didn't I!?\""},


{"lineNumber":175940,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……へへへっ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Hehehe.\""},


{"lineNumber":175941,"originalJapaneseLine":"「な、なんだ？　気持ち悪く笑いおって……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-what's with that creepy laugh...?\""},


{"lineNumber":175942,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、最終決戦だからって、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, even though it's the final battle,"},

{"lineNumber":175943,"originalJapaneseLine":"　緊張したりはしてないようだってな」","translatedEnglishLine":"it seems like there's no nervousness at all.\""},



{"lineNumber":175944,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ですが……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However...\""},

{"lineNumber":175945,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ケイブリス様との決着をつける前に、","translatedEnglishLine":"Before settling things with Lord Kavebris,"},

{"lineNumber":175946,"originalJapaneseLine":"　私達を素通りしてもらっては困ります」","translatedEnglishLine":"you can't just pass us by.\""},


{"lineNumber":175947,"originalJapaneseLine":"「これが貴方達と、マエリータ隊……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"This will be the last battle between you all and the Maelita Squad..."},

{"lineNumber":175948,"originalJapaneseLine":"　最後の戦いになるでしょう」","translatedEnglishLine":"the final fight, I suppose.\""},


{"lineNumber":175949,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお！　丁度いい！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh! Perfect timing!"},

{"lineNumber":175950,"originalJapaneseLine":"　テメェらとの因縁も今日限りだ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Our grudge with you ends today!\""},


{"lineNumber":175951,"originalJapaneseLine":"「嬉しいねぇ、嬉しいねぇ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I'm so glad, really glad!"},

{"lineNumber":175952,"originalJapaneseLine":"　決着をつけられる日が来るなんてよぉ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"To finally have a day to settle this!\""},


{"lineNumber":175953,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さあ、後はもう言葉は不要」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Now, there's no need for words."},

{"lineNumber":175954,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふっ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmph...\""},


{"lineNumber":175955,"originalJapaneseLine":"学者は初めて、ランス達に笑みを見せた。","translatedEnglishLine":"For the first time, the scholar showed a smile to Rance and the others."},


{"lineNumber":175956,"originalJapaneseLine":"「存分に戦いましょう！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Let's fight to our fullest!\""},


{"lineNumber":175957,"originalJapaneseLine":"ベズドグ山を見上げる二つの影があった。","translatedEnglishLine":"Two shadows looked up at Mount Bezudog."},


{"lineNumber":175958,"originalJapaneseLine":"「やれやれ……あの男は相変わらず、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Good grief... That man is as reckless as ever,"},

{"lineNumber":175959,"originalJapaneseLine":"　とんでもないことをしますね」","translatedEnglishLine":"always doing outrageous things.\""},


{"lineNumber":175960,"originalJapaneseLine":"「城ごと敵の本拠地に突貫ですか。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Charging the enemy's stronghold with the whole castle, huh."},

{"lineNumber":175961,"originalJapaneseLine":"　無茶苦茶というか、横着というか」","translatedEnglishLine":"It's absurd, or maybe just lazy.\""},


{"lineNumber":175962,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ですが……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However...\""},

{"lineNumber":175963,"originalJapaneseLine":"あの大胆さと行動の速さに、","translatedEnglishLine":"Everyone followed because of his boldness and quick actions."},

{"lineNumber":175964,"originalJapaneseLine":"　皆がついていったのも事実」","translatedEnglishLine":""},

{"lineNumber":175965,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひとりぼっちの貴方とは大違いですね」","translatedEnglishLine":"You're completely different from being all alone, aren't you?"},


{"lineNumber":175966,"originalJapaneseLine":"「どうしますか、アリオス。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What will you do, Ares?"},

{"lineNumber":175967,"originalJapaneseLine":"　また今回も先を越されますか？","translatedEnglishLine":"Will you be outpaced again this time?"},

{"lineNumber":175968,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いつものように」","translatedEnglishLine":"Like always?\""},


{"lineNumber":175969,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},


{"lineNumber":175970,"originalJapaneseLine":"「後も先もない」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"There is neither after nor before."},

{"lineNumber":175971,"originalJapaneseLine":"ただ、するべきことをするだけだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I will just do what must be done.\""},


{"lineNumber":175972,"originalJapaneseLine":"「行くぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Let's go.\""},


{"lineNumber":175973,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はいはい、勇者アリオス」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, alright, Hero Ares.\""},


{"lineNumber":175974,"originalJapaneseLine":"勇者アリオスと、その従者コーラ、","translatedEnglishLine":"Hero Ares and his servant Kora,"},


{"lineNumber":175975,"originalJapaneseLine":"この二人もまたベズドグ山に足を踏み入れた。","translatedEnglishLine":"these two also set foot inside Mount Bezudog."},


{"lineNumber":175976,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランス達がケイブリスの部屋を目指して、","translatedEnglishLine":"Rance and the others headed straight towards Kavebris's room,"},


{"lineNumber":175977,"originalJapaneseLine":"ベズドグ山内を真っ直ぐ進む。","translatedEnglishLine":"advancing straight through Mount Bezudog."},


{"lineNumber":175978,"originalJapaneseLine":"「む……？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm...?\""},


{"lineNumber":175979,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………ランス。来たか……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...Rance. You've come...\""},


{"lineNumber":175980,"originalJapaneseLine":"その眼前に、勇者の主従が立ちはだかった。","translatedEnglishLine":"Before them, the hero and his retainer stood in their way."},


{"lineNumber":175981,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぬ、貴様……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-you...!"},


{"lineNumber":175982,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんてしつこい野郎だ。また現れたか」","translatedEnglishLine":"What a persistent bastard. You've appeared again.\""},


{"lineNumber":175983,"originalJapaneseLine":"抜き身のエスクードソードを手にしたアリオスに、","translatedEnglishLine":"Ares drew his escudo sword,"},


{"lineNumber":175984,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスもさっさとカオスを抜く。","translatedEnglishLine":"and Rance quickly drew Chaos as well."},


{"lineNumber":175985,"originalJapaneseLine":"「このくそ忙しいのに、貴様に関わる暇などないわ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I'm damn busy, and I don't have time to deal with you."},

{"lineNumber":175986,"originalJapaneseLine":"　とりあえず言っておいてやるが、失せろ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll just say this for now: get lost.\""},


{"lineNumber":175987,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ケイブリスを倒しても、何も変わらない」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Even if we defeat Kavebris, nothing will change.\""},


{"lineNumber":175988,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あん？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh?\""},


{"lineNumber":175989,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王を……リトルプリンセスを殺さなければ、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Unless we kill the Demon King... the Little Princess,"},

{"lineNumber":175990,"originalJapaneseLine":"　人類には、平和が訪れないんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"peace will never come to humanity.\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 待ったをかける声が届いた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A voice calling for a pause reached them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あぁん？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この聞き覚えのあるような、ないような声は……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This voice sounds familiar... or does it?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お久し振りですね、皆さん」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's been a while, everyone."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「マエリータ隊！　参上！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The Maelita Squad! Here to serve!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お前らは！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You guys are!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……マヨネーズ隊だったか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...the Mayonnaise Squad, was it?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「マエリータ隊だ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's the Maelita Squad!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、そう名乗っただろうが！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I just said so, didn't I!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……へへへっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Hehehe."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「な、なんだ？　気持ち悪く笑いおって……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-what's with that creepy laugh...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、最終決戦だからって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No, even though it's the final battle,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 緊張したりはしてないようだってな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it seems like there's no nervousness at all."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様との決着をつける前に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before settling things with Lord Kavebris,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私達を素通りしてもらっては困ります」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you can't just pass us by."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これが貴方達と、マエリータ隊……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This will be the last battle between you all and the Maelita Squad...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最後の戦いになるでしょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the final fight, I suppose."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おお！　丁度いい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh! Perfect timing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テメェらとの因縁も今日限りだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our grudge with you ends today!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「嬉しいねぇ、嬉しいねぇ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm so glad, really glad!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 決着をつけられる日が来るなんてよぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To finally have a day to settle this!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあ、後はもう言葉は不要」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Now, there's no need for words.
"Hmph..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 学者は初めて、ランス達に笑みを見せた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: For the first time, the scholar showed a smile to Rance and the others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「存分に戦いましょう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's fight to our fullest!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ベズドグ山を見上げる二つの影があった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two shadows looked up at Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やれやれ……あの男は相変わらず、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Good grief... That man is as reckless as ever,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とんでもないことをしますね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: always doing outrageous things."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「城ごと敵の本拠地に突貫ですか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Charging the enemy's stronghold with the whole castle, huh.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 無茶苦茶というか、横着というか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's absurd, or maybe just lazy."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの大胆さと行動の速さに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone followed because of his boldness and quick actions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 皆がついていったのも事実」
「ひとりぼっちの貴方とは大違いですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're completely different from being all alone, aren't you?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どうしますか、アリオス。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What will you do, Ares?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: また今回も先を越されますか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Will you be outpaced again this time?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつものように」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like always?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「後も先もない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "There is neither after nor before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ、するべきことをするだけだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I will just do what must be done."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「行くぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's go."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はいはい、勇者アリオス」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, alright, Hero Ares."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者アリオスと、その従者コーラ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hero Ares and his servant Kora,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この二人もまたベズドグ山に足を踏み入れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: these two also set foot inside Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達がケイブリスの部屋を目指して、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others headed straight towards Kavebris's room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ベズドグ山内を真っ直ぐ進む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: advancing straight through Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………ランス。来たか……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Rance. You've come..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その眼前に、勇者の主従が立ちはだかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before them, the hero and his retainer stood in their way.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぬ、貴様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Y-you...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんてしつこい野郎だ。また現れたか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a persistent bastard. You've appeared again."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 抜き身のエスクードソードを手にしたアリオスに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ares drew his escudo sword,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスもさっさとカオスを抜く。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Rance quickly drew Chaos as well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「このくそ忙しいのに、貴様に関わる暇などないわ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm damn busy, and I don't have time to deal with you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とりあえず言っておいてやるが、失せろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll just say this for now: get lost."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ケイブリスを倒しても、何も変わらない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even if we defeat Kavebris, nothing will change."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔王を……リトルプリンセスを殺さなければ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Unless we kill the Demon King... the Little Princess,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類には、平和が訪れないんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: peace will never come to humanity."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……へへへっ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Hehehe."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「な、なんだ？　気持ち悪く笑いおって……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "W-what's with that creepy laugh...?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、最終決戦だからって、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No, even though it's the final battle,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 緊張したりはしてないようだってな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it seems like there's no nervousness at all."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケイブリス様との決着をつける前に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before settling things with Lord Kavebris,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私達を素通りしてもらっては困ります」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: you can't just pass us by."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これが貴方達と、マエリータ隊……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "This will be the last battle between you all and the Maelita Squad...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最後の戦いになるでしょう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the final fight, I suppose."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おお！　丁度いい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh! Perfect timing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テメェらとの因縁も今日限りだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Our grudge with you ends today!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「嬉しいねぇ、嬉しいねぇ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm so glad, really glad!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 決着をつけられる日が来るなんてよぉ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To finally have a day to settle this!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあ、後はもう言葉は不要」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Now, there's no need for words.
"Hmph..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 学者は初めて、ランス達に笑みを見せた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: For the first time, the scholar showed a smile to Rance and the others.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「存分に戦いましょう！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's fight to our fullest!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ベズドグ山を見上げる二つの影があった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Two shadows looked up at Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「やれやれ……あの男は相変わらず、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Good grief... That man is as reckless as ever,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とんでもないことをしますね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: always doing outrageous things."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「城ごと敵の本拠地に突貫ですか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Charging the enemy's stronghold with the whole castle, huh.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 無茶苦茶というか、横着というか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's absurd, or maybe just lazy."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの大胆さと行動の速さに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone followed because of his boldness and quick actions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 皆がついていったのも事実」
「ひとりぼっちの貴方とは大違いですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're completely different from being all alone, aren't you?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どうしますか、アリオス。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What will you do, Ares?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: また今回も先を越されますか？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Will you be outpaced again this time?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつものように」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like always?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「後も先もない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "There is neither after nor before.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただ、するべきことをするだけだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I will just do what must be done."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「行くぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Let's go."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はいはい、勇者アリオス」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Alright, alright, Hero Ares."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 勇者アリオスと、その従者コーラ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hero Ares and his servant Kora,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この二人もまたベズドグ山に足を踏み入れた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: these two also set foot inside Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達がケイブリスの部屋を目指して、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance and the others headed straight towards Kavebris's room,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ベズドグ山内を真っ直ぐ進む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: advancing straight through Mount Bezudog.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「…………ランス。来たか……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...Rance. You've come..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その眼前に、勇者の主従が立ちはだかった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Before them, the hero and his retainer stood in their way.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぬ、貴様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Y-you...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんてしつこい野郎だ。また現れたか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What a persistent bastard. You've appeared again."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 抜き身のエスクードソードを手にしたアリオスに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ares drew his escudo sword,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスもさっさとカオスを抜く。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Rance quickly drew Chaos as well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「このくそ忙しいのに、貴様に関わる暇などないわ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'm damn busy, and I don't have time to deal with you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とりあえず言っておいてやるが、失せろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll just say this for now: get lost."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ケイブリスを倒しても、何も変わらない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even if we defeat Kavebris, nothing will change."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Huh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「魔王を……リトルプリンセスを殺さなければ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Unless we kill the Demon King... the Little Princess,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人類には、平和が訪れないんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: peace will never come to humanity."
